title: Subaru wants to ‘Share the Love’ in 2015 by donating $15 million to charity
text:
Subaru wants to ‘Share the Love’ in 2015 by donating $15 million to charity 
Published By: DigitalTrends.com - Today 
Subaru has announced that its Share the Love event will return for the eighth straight year in 2015, running from November 19 to January 2. ...
